column1: Previous User Stories
Story Title
Setup namecheap domain
Decide on Project topic
Find sources
Research models, relationships, attributes
Connect Flask/Docker app to GCP
Setup basic site landing page and nav bar
As a user, I want to see available crates in the game.
As a user, I want to see available vehicle bodies in the game.
As a user, I want to see available in-game decals.
As a user, I want to see available paint finishes.
As a user, I want to see items grouped into categories.
As a user, I want to see rarities of items.
As a user, I want to see availability of items (when they were available, can I get them now).
As a developer, I want references to each attribute so that I can easily look up related items.

Story Title
As a user, I want to see which crates contain which items.
As a user, I want to see more links on the front page in addition to the navigation menu.
As a user, I want to see the contributions of each team member.
As a user, I want to see a list of all of the tools used to create the application.
As a user, I want to see why this site was created.
As a user, I want to see the name of the site on the front page.
As a PS4 user, I want to see player stats for PS4 players.
As an Xbox user, I want to see player stats for Xbox players.
As a PC user, I want to see player stats for Steam players.
As a user, I want to view information about the game the database is based on.
